g-aero/gbs\n  summary: Geometry BSplines - A C++ header library for BSplines curves and surfaces\n  license: LGPL-3.0-or-later\n  license_file: LICENSE.LGPLv3\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - szebos\n    - ssg-aero\n",
